         Since the dot reduction of damage was removed, there, are even some other ways.</P><P>Long Pull:<BR>Darkness<BR>Fast Dot (posion line)<BR>Another dot (your choice)<BR>Send in pet<BR>Fear<BR>Refresh Darkness<BR>Refresh Fear as needed</P><P>This is for long pulls does two things<BR>A puts a dent into the mob before it gets to your pet, and also allows you to worry a little less about your pets life, since while your kiting the mob back your pet is healing and ready to whip some ass as. <BR>   Of Course souly outdoors only unless you fine a nice pathing bug.</P><P>But just my two sense there are reasons to Dr00d kite then start the fear kite, makes for faster killing IMHO as I've seen, but zones very as it where any way.</P><P><BR>Metiphisto<BR>56 Defiler</P><P><BR>"I play with dead people....."<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
